    @* ============================== Proof strip ============================== *@

    <section class="bb-proof">
        <div><strong>Framework parity</strong><span>every <code>&#64;page</code> template matches identically</span></div>
        <div><strong>Prerender-ready</strong><span>Server, WebAssembly &amp; Auto render modes</span></div>
